01:22:36,411 --> 01:22:38,355
I walked with 30, 40 colleagues,

1362
01:22:38,455 --> 01:22:41,066
and we tried to work out
where we needed to be,

1363
01:22:41,166 --> 01:22:45,337
and how we needed to shoot
all of the following and in what order.

